headline: DoorDash offers fulfillment service for retailers
summary: DoorDash on Tuesday unveiled a fulfillment service for retailers, a road-capable delivery robot, an autonomous delivery platform and a smart-scale device to ensure order accuracy. The post DoorDash offers fulfillment service for retailers appeared first on FreightWaves.
